										<div class="elementor-slides-wrapper elementor-main-swiper swiper" role="region" aria-roledescription="carousel" aria-label="Slides" dir="ltr" data-animation="">
				<div class="swiper-wrapper elementor-slides">
										<div class="elementor-repeater-item-9d2b3a7 swiper-slide" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide"><div class="swiper-slide-bg" role="img" aria-label="Sth Walker Ck-92 resized"></div><div class="elementor-background-overlay"></div><div class="swiper-slide-inner" ><div class="swiper-slide-contents"><div class="elementor-slide-heading">Strength in Execution</div><div class="elementor-slide-description">At Stanmore, we invest in performance and operational excellence to deliver consistent value for our stakeholders and communities.</div><a href="https://stanmore.au/investors/" class="elementor-button elementor-slide-button elementor-size-sm">Find out more</a></div></div></div><div class="elementor-repeater-item-875bcd2 swiper-slide" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide"><div class="swiper-slide-bg" role="img" aria-label="Sth Walker Creek-96 resized"></div><div class="elementor-background-overlay"></div><div class="swiper-slide-inner" ><div class="swiper-slide-contents"><div class="elementor-slide-heading">Our People</div><div class="elementor-slide-description">Our fast-paced, agile culture is built on care, opportunity, and real outcomes. We back our people to lead, grow, and thrive.</div><a href="https://stanmore.au/about-us/our-people/" class="elementor-button elementor-slide-button elementor-size-sm">Find out more</a></div></div></div><div class="elementor-repeater-item-32fcc91 swiper-slide" role="group" aria-roledescription="slide"><div class="swiper-slide-bg" role="img" aria-label="Stanmore-Embracing-our-Sustainability-Journey"></div><div class="elementor-background-overlay"></div><a class="swiper-slide-inner" href="https://stanmore.au/sustainability/"><div class="swiper-slide-contents"><div class="elementor-slide-heading">Embracing our Sustainability Journey</div><div class="elementor-slide-description">Sustainability is central to everything we do - guided by our five-year roadmap and a firm commitment to best practice and continuous improvement.</div><div  class="elementor-button elementor-slide-button elementor-size-sm">Read more</div></div></a></div>				</div>
																				<div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
												</div>
								</div>
				</div>
		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-97f3a82 e-flex e-con-boxed elementor-invisible e-con e-parent" data-id="97f3a82" data-element_type="container" data-settings="{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;,&quot;animation&quot;:&quot;fadeIn&quot;}">
					<div class="e-con-inner">
				<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-0a2d387 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading" data-id="0a2d387" data-element_type="widget" data-widget_type="heading.default">
					<h4 class="elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default">Stanmore Resources is an Australian company with world-class operations and exploration projects in the Bowen Basin. We’re proud to be <b>one of Australia’s largest suppliers of metallurgical coal to global markets.</b> </h4>				</div>
					</div>
				</div>
		<div class="elementor-element elementor-element-41c12b2 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent" data-id="41c12b2" data-element_type="container">
					<div class="e-con-inner">
